verbose_text: The EtMIC2 gene or rEtMIC2 proteins expressed in prokaryotic, plant or Pichia pastoris expression systems have been used as either a DNA vaccine or sub-unit vaccine to immunize chickens against a homologous challenge in several early studies [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
